drink_amount

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
drink_amount -  This method drinks a certain amount of the liquid in the container.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int drink_amount(int drinking,
                 object player)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^drinking%^RESET%^ - the amount to drink 

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/vessel.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method drinks a certain amount of the liquid in the container.
It will do all the fudging for being in combat and drinking too
much, as well as dropping the bottle and so on.
.EP

